BT 1 0 0 1 0 15 Tm 12 TL /F2 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (The Zeno Effect) Tj /F1 9 Tf ( \(Misra & Sudarshan, 1977\): Frequent observation of an unstable quantum system can SLOW its decay.) Tj T* (Measure a radioactive atom every microsecond and it decays more slowly than if you leave it alone.) Tj T* ET
